author: Inside Edition
description:
Sponsored Content by RoC Skincare.
 
Inside Edition teamed up with RoC® Skincare and its partner, dermatologist Dr. Sheila Farhang, for anti-aging tips. She says aging, lack of sunscreen and excessive and repeated movement can cause deep wrinkles in the neck. Dr. Farhang recommends RoC's Firming Serum Stick as an at-home, non-invasive lift for your face and neck.
title: Say Goodbye to Turkey Neck! Dermatologist Shares Her Top Anti-Aging Secret

author: Inside Edition
description: Luigi Mangione, who's accused of assassinating UnitedHealthcare CEO Brian Thompson, won a major courtroom victory Tuesday. A judge dismissed Mangione's terrorism charges that carry life prison terms, saying the evidence was "legally insufficient." The 27-year-old accused assassin is still facing state and federal murder charges and could get the death penalty if convicted. Crowds outside the courthouse waved banners and chanted loud enough to be heard inside.
title: Luigi Mangione's Terrorism Charges Dismissed By New York Judge

author: Inside Edition
description: Emotions are still running high over Charlie Kirk's assassination. One New Jersey nurse was suspended when she challenged a doctor who she claims said Kirk "deserved to die." Nurse Lexi Kinzel was reinstated and the doctor resigned. Beni Rae Harmony, an anchor at an Illinois station says she was suspended when she went off-script and made an on-air tribute to Kirk. She has now resigned. Meanwhile, Democrats in the Utah State House say they're getting blasted with hateful messages.
title: Emotions Still Running High After Charlie Kirk's Assassination

author: Inside Edition
description: President Donald Trump and First Lady Melania left the White House Tuesday to head to London for a state visit. In the wake of the assassination of Charlie Kirk, concerns over security have heightened. Like French president Emmanuel Macron, Trump will ride with King Charles in an open-top carriage, only this time it will take place within the walls of Windsor Castle, where the state dinner will be held. Inside Edition spoke with security expert Duncan Gardham.
title: President Trump And Melania Head To London Amid Security Concerns

author: Inside Edition
description: Six months before his death, legendary star Robert Redford came out of retirement to play a prison inmate on AMC's "Dark Winds." At age 88, Redford wasn’t supposed to have any dialogue, but he couldn't resist. Redford died Tuesday at age 89 at his ranch in Utah, but little is known about the circumstances surrounding his death. Over the past few years, the film icon had become a recluse. His wife, Sibylle Szaggars, released a recent photo along with a statement.
title: Legendary Star Robert Redford Dead At 89

author: Inside Edition
description: Social media is filled with 100 days till Christmas posts. Marissa Silva is editor of the Toy Insider and tells Inside Edition that this year, there's a reason to get an early start. Items like Legos and the Nintendo Switch 2 are going to be really popular. Silva says that you can't go wrong with Hot Wheels. Target says some of the best prices will come October 5 through October 11. Best Buy's 48-hour flash sale kicks off on September 27.
title: 100 Days Till Christmas: Getting A Head Start On Gifts

author: Inside Edition
description: Police bodycam footage captured the moment an outrageous act of vandalism was discovered at an elementary school. With guns drawn, officers made their way through the school. Tables were overturned, books ripped from shelves, and graffiti covered shelves and doors. On Monday, a 12-year-old and a 13-year-old boy were charged. Volusia County Sheriff Mike Chitwood said the boys' moms turned them in and the boys admitted to breaking into the school.
title: Teen Boys, 12 And 13, Charged In School Vandalism Case

author: Inside Edition
description: Reports say the Orange County Sheriff's Office in Florida was sent to help a homeowner who called 911 to say he was the victim of a home invasion. Bodycam from the deputy shows that the shot was fired as the homeowner was trying to open the door for them. Inside Edition Digital’s Mara Montalbano has more.
title: Deputy Accidentally Shoots Homeowner Who Called 911 For Help: Reports

author: Inside Edition
description: The Australian government approved the vaccine to be administered by vets in hospitals and clinics, as well as in the wild.
title: Koalas Get Chlamydia Vaccine #shorts

author: Inside Edition
description: Robert Hocevar was arrested during a police raid at his home outside Cleveland, Ohio, and later convicted of stalking seven women.
title: Video Camera Installer Convicted of Stalking #shorts

author: Inside Edition
description: It was supposed to be a short stop for a boat to refuel, but it would never make it far from the dock. The Macomb County Sheriff in Michigan says a couple and their dog were on the boat when it exploded. They had just finished refueling and pulled away from the dock when the unthinkable happened. Officials say the two human occupants were thrown from the vessel and had minor injuries. Inside Edition Digital’s Mara Montalbano has more.
title: 2 People Hurt, Dog Dead After Boat Explosion In Michigan

author: Inside Edition
description: Diane Wright was walking her 4-month-old Shih Tzu, Dax, by a creek outside Tampa when an alligator suddenly appeared and lunged for the dog. Incredibly, the gator's teeth clamped down on Dax's AirTag on his collar, that's when Wright jumped in and punched the gator in the eye. She was left with bites on her forearm. Wildlife experts took the alligator away. Wright spoke with Inside Edition's Alison Hall.
title: Woman Punches Alligator In Eye After It Lunges For Her Dog

author: Inside Edition
description: In a new documentary "Ruby & Jodi: A Cult of Sin and Influence," Investigation Discovery uncovers how Jodi Hildebrandt became the mastermind of the two mothers.
title: Jodi Hildebrandt's Niece Speaks Out About 'Abusive' Experience #shorts
